Q: In the diagram, $PRT$ and $QRS$ are straight lines. What is the value of $x$? [asy]
import olympiad;
import math;

size(6cm); // ADJUST

pair r = (0, 0);
pair t = dir(-55);
pair s = dir(-55 - 70);
pair p = dir(-55 + 180);
real qr = Sin(70) / Sin(40);

pair q = qr * dir(-55 - 70 + 180);

